PrecisOrder fixing WEDNESDAY, SEPTEMBER 1st, 1999, as the day upon which this Act [Bill C-25] being chapter 35 of the Statutes of Canada, 1998, shall COME INTO FORCE, except for sections 4, 7, 10, 12 of the Act, section 250 to 250.53 of the National Defence Act, as enacted by section 82 of the Act, and sections 103, 104, 106, 107, 122 and 123 and 125 of the Act.
